snippet.title: Learn How To Pronounce Amber Heard
snippet.description:

About Us:
School of Pronunciation is a free English video pronunciation guide. We started this project in June 2019, with the intention of providing ourselves a reference for American English pronunciation. American pronunciation is one of the world’s most widely used. Our mission is one of confidence; to give our subscribers of all backgrounds the ability to be confident communicators on demand. At the moment, our pronunciation practice style involves us saying the word, then giving subscribers time to repeat the word aloud. This repetitive approach is believed to shorten the learning curve of subscribers whose goal is to speak English like a native. We aim to provide clear and accurate pronunciation of words that new English speakers commonly struggle with. We also strive to remain abreast of words that appear in the latest trending issues.
